When Ylva activates her MasterΓÇÖs Form, she channels the spectral chaos of the Wild Hunt. The air around her fills with the phantom sounds of baying hounds and thundering hooves. This auditory hallucination overwhelms the senses of her enemies, explaining the "Push" effect as they stumble back from the ghostly stampede radiating from her spinning axe.
